WEBVTT

00:00.299 --> 00:01.957
Hi, this is BLACKPINK.

00:02.121 --> 00:04.703
And we want to share an important message with you all.

00:05.366 --> 00:09.032
We are the first generation to have grown up in the digital age,...

00:09.403 --> 00:10.947
...and that makes us unique.

00:11.472 --> 00:15.005
Since we have grown up connected with each other through technology,...

00:15.381 --> 00:18.742
...we have a lot in common regardless of where we live on Earth.

00:19.191 --> 00:21.305
And today, we're united once again...

00:21.435 --> 00:25.565
...as we're facing a common problem associated with the times that we live in.

00:26.131 --> 00:27.691
I, BLACKPINK.

00:28.347 --> 00:30.433
Blinks, our generation.

00:31.368 --> 00:32.990
Hundreds of millions of us.

00:33.894 --> 00:36.475
Those of us who will one day inherit this Earth.

